\left\vert{\frac1{\lambda_{k+1}}}\right\vert=\min\limits_{y\in{\mathbb R}^{k+1},\,\left\lVert y\right\lVert_2=1}\left\lVert{X_{k+1}y}\right\lVert_2^2\,,
